            <div type="transcript" id="P96-37">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I had a daily bliss</l>
                    <l>I half indifferent viewed,</l>
                    <l>Till sudden I perceived it stir, </l>
                    <l>It grew as I pursued,</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Till when, around a crag,</l>
                    <l>It wasted from my sight,</l>
                    <l>Enlarged beyond my utmost scope,</l>
                    <l>I learned its sweetness right.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
